data.title: Dive into anything
data.text:
Nobody can help the guy as obviously they need their own masks.

I saw this in early 1990’s in the U.K. I was born in 1988 so at a guess I would say I saw this between 1992 and 1995. The movie / show could of been older though it’s just a vague memory I have as a kid.

English speaking so either British or American. I’m thinking it was American
